README file

A way to run scheduled task on joomla with or without crontab


without crontab

The Zoombie system plugin when alive check for little zoombies to run

with crontab

you can schedule the CLI app for check for little zoombies to run



the little zoombies

 - files backup 

 - db backup
 
 - site checksum
 
 - slicomments spam detector

 - users spam detector
 
 - Anti Malware scan script
